This is a support area for features this project provides. It mainly focuses on restoring features, that were previously part of my legacy add-ons on AMO.

This is not a "request what you want" area!
Join the discussion thread to talk and ask questions about what is or could be possible.
--> General discussions, feedback, questions belong here (v2)
--> https://github.com/Aris-t2/CustomCSSforFx/issues/41

Read the "how to report an issue instructions" before filing an issue report.
--> READ 'how to report issues properly' BEFORE REPORTING ISSUES!
--> https://github.com/Aris-t2/CustomCSSforFx/issues/4

By filing an issue report you confirm to have read and understood the above and all "how to report an issue" instructions.
False/invalid issue reports might get closed without further notice.
